Access functions are provided in the accompanying package 'deeptime'.

name: r-deeptimedata
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}
{% set posix = "m2-" if win else "" %}

package:
  name: r-deeptimedata
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/deeptimedata_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/deeptimedata/deeptimedata_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b9a0f78e7d0cc9e71678e7f3a852c71d59943bf472d8f055b79d9091916d37a6

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/
  missing_dso_whitelist:
    - '*/R.dll'        # [win]
    - '*/Rblas.dll'    # [win]
    - '*/Rlapack.dll'  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip  # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}  # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('deeptimedata')"  # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('deeptimedata')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/willgearty/deeptimedata
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  summary: |
    Geologic pattern data from <https://ngmdb.usgs.gov/fgdc_gds/geolsymstd.php>.
    Access functions are provided in the accompanying package 'deeptime'.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'
  dev_url: https://github.com/willgearty/deeptimedata
  doc_url: https://williamgearty.com/deeptimedata/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - willgearty
